#' @return A results object containing:
#' \tabular{llllll}{
#'   \code{results$tblTS} \tab \tab \tab \tab \tab a table \cr
#'   \code{results$rpplot} \tab \tab \tab \tab \tab an image \cr
#'   \code{results$rnetplot} \tab \tab \tab \tab \tab an image \cr
